

=Bio=

Writer and consultant  in the domain of indigenous rights, national director of Centro de Estudios  Aplicados a los Derechos Económicos, Sociales y Culturales (CEADESC) and  profesor of semiotics, philosophy of language and epistomology at different  universities. He  investigates new paradigms,  mega projects and issues related to neo-extractivsm.


